1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,980
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 15 =

20
00:01:42,580 --> 00:01:43,380
Okay.

21
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:51,980
I received this letter from Yuansheng

22
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:52,860
at nightfall.

23
00:01:53,460 --> 00:01:55,100
He also wrote one to me.

24
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,380
The date on the letter

25
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:57,860
is five or six days ago.

26
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,340
= Landlady of the Restaurant of Breeze, Zhang Lihua =
He said

27
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:00,980
he’s sure his brother

28
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:01,700
was sold by his aunt-in-law

29
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:02,500
in collusion with the county magistrate.

30
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:07,700
= Wang Mansion =

31
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:17,140
= Letter from Yuansheng =
I should not disturb you so late,

32
00:02:17,940 --> 00:02:19,060
= Wang Zeng, courtesy name Xiaoxian =
but this is an important issue.

33
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,620
If my memory serves me right,

34
00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:23,660
a few months ago,

35
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:24,860
this magistrate

36
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,540
is the best in the performance review

37
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:29,100
and has been recommended to come to the Capital.

38
00:02:29,780 --> 00:02:30,820
If what Liang Yuansheng said

39
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,020
in the letter

40
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:33,180
can be testified,

41
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:34,460
then

42
00:02:35,140 --> 00:02:37,220
I think the reviewing process

43
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:40,460
should be checked closely

44
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:42,020
for any bribes and factions.

45
00:02:45,660 --> 00:02:46,860
Censor Han, you mean...

46
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:51,100
I suggest

47
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:54,380
to seal all the documents

48
00:02:54,380 --> 00:02:55,260
in the reviewing process of this magistrate.

49
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,980
If the Judge and Prosecutor of this county

50
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,900
finds out what Liang Yuansheng said is true,

51
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:02,860
then we should investigate

52
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:06,460
all the officials responsible

53
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:07,260
for reviewing the performance of this magistrate.

54
00:03:07,860 --> 00:03:10,340
Did they fail to fulfill their duty
or were they bribed?

55
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:15,460
I ask to discuss at the court

56
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:17,780
the adultery of the magistrate of Liaocheng

57
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:20,540
who plundered people’s property,
took bribes and bent the law.

58
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:23,140
If a county magistrate took bribes
and bent the law,

59
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,980
if it’s been testified

60
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:27,300
with clear evidence,

61
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:29,420
just dismiss him from the office or imprison him

62
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,020
according to the law.

63
00:03:31,380 --> 00:03:32,700
It’s not needed to be discussed at the court.

64
00:03:37,260 --> 00:03:38,260
Your Majesty,

65
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,660
the bribery of a county magistrate

66
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,900
does not need to be discussed at the court,

67
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,660
but this magistrate

68
00:03:46,340 --> 00:03:48,500
is ranked first

69
00:03:48,980 --> 00:03:50,020
in his recent performance review.

70
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,260
He’s been recommended for promotion

71
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,660
by his superior and three officials at the court.

72
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:55,860
If this matter was not exposed

73
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,260
by an ordinary people

74
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:58,980
who appealed for justice,

75
00:03:59,140 --> 00:04:00,340
this county magistrate

76
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:04,060
would soon come to the Capital to take his post.

77
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:15,380
Then let’s discuss about it.

78
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:18,260
Officials at the court

79
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:20,380
must be proposing a lot of important issues.

80
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:21,940
It’s almost dark now.

81
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:23,900
His Majesty is still in the Hall of Arch.

82
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:25,460
What things

83
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:27,380
do you think they are proposing?

84
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:33,700
You are just like a piece of wood.

85
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:38,300
Just now Censor Han

86
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:41,180
accused the magistrate for bribery,

87
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:43,020
with complete evidence.

88
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:46,940
Han also accused the magistrate’s superior

89
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:50,380
and three officials who recommended him

90
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:53,340
of making up evidence and hiding mistakes

91
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:56,660
with actual evidence.

92
00:04:58,180 --> 00:05:02,340
But you criticized me directly

93
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:04,260
at the court

94
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:06,460
in front of His Majesty

95
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:10,740
for manipulating the promotion
and demotion of officials.

96
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:12,860
Tell me,

97
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:16,620
do you have any evidence

98
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:18,300
showing that I accept bribes?

99
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:21,740
If you have any,
I am willing to take my punishment.

100
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:22,820
If you don’t,

101
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:26,300
then you are slandering the Prime Minister.

102
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:35,740
We

103
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:39,900
don’t have evidence showing you take bribes.

104
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:43,980
But

105
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,180
are those officials

106
00:05:47,660 --> 00:05:49,740
with clear evidence showing they are corrupted

107
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:53,780
your subordinates that you trust?

108
00:05:58,540 --> 00:06:00,180
As the Prime Minister,

109
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:02,700
I have tremendous affairs to attend to.

110
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:06,420
I can’t be attentive to all the details.

111
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:11,060
Maybe you didn’t take

112
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:12,820
anything from your subordinates,

113
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:17,300
but if you were not biased and narrow-minded,

114
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:19,660
if you didn’t demote
or strike off upright officials,

115
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,300
if you didn’t put officials
who know nothing more than building up factions

116
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:22,900
and putting their personal interests prior
to everything,

117
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:26,620
how could that county magistrate

118
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:28,220
who committed adultery and bribery

119
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:31,420
be reviewed as a good official?

120
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:37,900
The Prime Minister who failed to perform
his duty like this

121
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:41,540
is even worse and more harmful

122
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,820
than those who take bribes!

123
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:48,020
He should be killed for his intention!

124
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:00,060
What you said

125
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:01,780
left Lv Yijian no room for dispute.

126
00:07:02,180 --> 00:07:03,340
I also agree on what you said.

127
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:06,260
Although Lv Yijian made huge contributions

128
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,340
to the court,

129
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,700
and there’s no evidence showing he took bribes,

130
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:10,300
but I still announced to punish him.

131
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:12,340
But I just made the announcement yesterday,

132
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:14,020
now you came to ask for

133
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:16,060
being exiled out of the Capital with Lv Yijian?

134
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:18,180
Do you think

135
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,860
what you said about Lv Yijian is wrong

136
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:21,780
so I should revoke my order?

137
00:07:23,460 --> 00:07:25,540
I meant every word I said.

138
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:29,220
Your Majesty made a timely and great decision.

139
00:07:29,620 --> 00:07:30,340
So do you think

140
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:31,900
I didn’t give Lv Yijian enough punishment

141
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:32,860
and you are unsatisfied with me?

142
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,060
No, no way.

143
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:36,380
I asked for punishment

144
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:40,860
because I am guilty.

145
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:46,540
You’ve made his guilt

146
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,300
very clear.

147
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:50,700
Now you are telling me you should be punished too.

148
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:51,980
Tell me,

149
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:53,300
what did you do wrong?

150
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:55,180
Can it be so wrong that

151
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,500
you should be punished the same way

152
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,460
as Lv Yijian?

153
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:00,740
This case has been widely spread

154
00:08:00,740 --> 00:08:02,340
from Liaocheng to Kaifeng,

155
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,140
and many officials are involved in it.

156
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:05,700
If all the rumors among people

157
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:07,700
and all kinds of exaggerated stories

158
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:08,980
are spread out…

159
00:08:09,220 --> 00:08:10,820
The kid is in the palace now.

160
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:15,620
Although Deputy Officer Deng

161
00:08:15,860 --> 00:08:16,780
who’s responsible for recruiting boys to the palace

162
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:18,260
won’t force them,

163
00:08:19,140 --> 00:08:20,300
but he was reckless in recruiting.

164
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:21,340
If it’s spread,

165
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:22,820
it will sound like the royal family

166
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:24,540
is robbing boys from ordinary people.

167
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:29,660
Censor Han, don’t worry.

168
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:31,660
I’ve asked this kid

169
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:35,660
when he was punished

170
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:36,700
for violating the taboo,

171
00:08:36,980 --> 00:08:38,420
if he has any families outside,

172
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:39,820
and if he feels guilty to his ancestors

173
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:42,260
when I changed his name.

174
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:45,460
He said once he stepped in the palace,

175
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,500
he doesn’t have any father, ancestor or brother.

176
00:08:47,580 --> 00:08:49,180
The other day, I asked him if he knew

177
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:52,380
Liang Yuansheng.

178
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:56,780
He said

179
00:08:57,900 --> 00:09:00,820
Huaiji didn’t hear that name.

180
00:09:05,060 --> 00:09:06,980
Those officials responsible for reviews

181
00:09:07,420 --> 00:09:09,580
were all promoted by Lv Yijian.

182
00:09:10,740 --> 00:09:12,340
They dare to distort the truth

183
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,500
and turn things upside down

184
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:16,300
just because Lv Yijian manipulates the court

185
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:18,060
and responds harshly to upright and loyal officials

186
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:20,340
like Fan Zhongyan.

187
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:24,900
Even if he didn’t take a cent,

188
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:26,500
as the Prime Minister,

189
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:27,900
he failed to do his duty.

190
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:32,820
I am the Deputy Prime Minister,

191
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:35,700
since 1032 A.D.,

192
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:38,140
I’ve been working in the cabinet with Lv Yijian

193
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,500
to manage political affairs.

194
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:41,780
How can I be innocent

195
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:45,700
if he failed to do his duty?

196
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:50,300
Since 1033 A.D.

197
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:52,660
when Fan Zhongyan was demoted out of the Capital,

198
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,660
the disputes over political opinions at the court

199
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:56,460
are always regarded as disputes between factions

200
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:57,820
especially when they are involved with impeachment

201
00:09:58,220 --> 00:10:00,060
or support to Lv Yijian.

202
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:03,740
Xiaoxian,

203
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:06,220
in your whole career,

204
00:10:06,860 --> 00:10:08,660
you always considered yourself as unbiased.

205
00:10:09,140 --> 00:10:11,860
You don’t want to be suspected

206
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:14,100
for benefiting from the faction dispute.

207
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:22,500
You are not guilty, so you shouldn’t be punished.

208
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:32,260
But because of your self-discipline
and introspection,

209
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:34,260
you set a good example

210
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:36,740
to all officials at the court.

211
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:48,580
I’ll send you to Yunzhou

212
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:50,500
as the Left General

213
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,660
and the Grand Scholar of the Hall of Consultation.

214
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:04,540
Zhigui,

215
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:07,420
Zhigui.

216
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:10,060
Do you know Yuansheng was sentenced
with banishment?

217
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,580
I am writing a proposal for him...

218
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,300
I know.

219
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:13,940
This is what I expected.

220
00:11:15,700 --> 00:11:16,780
What you expected?

221
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,980
Since he detained an appointed official

222
00:11:19,980 --> 00:11:21,060
and instigated others,

223
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:22,220
he broke the law,

224
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:24,500
but his aunt-in-law colluded
with the county magistrate for money

225
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:25,980
and even sold his brother.

226
00:11:26,140 --> 00:11:27,180
He took the letter of his uncle

227
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:28,540
and mother to seek for justice,

228
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:29,700
but what he got in return was 40 canings

229
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:30,580
and being driven away.

230
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:31,940
Even His Majesty said

231
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:33,780
the people were forced to do so by the officials.

232
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:37,580
It is justifiable,

233
00:11:38,620 --> 00:11:40,380
that’s why he is excused from canings and tattoo,

234
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:42,500
his property will be returned,

235
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,340
and he will be banished for only 2 years.

236
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:45,580
But...

237
00:11:46,780 --> 00:11:48,340
He can’t be excused from all his punishments.

238
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:51,980
First of all,

239
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:53,580
Law means something.

240
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:54,860
Second,

241
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:56,980
if there’s no punishment for him,

242
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:58,460
does that mean the court

243
00:11:58,460 --> 00:12:00,060
allows the people

244
00:12:00,060 --> 00:12:01,020
to appeal for justice with violence,

245
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,820
and they can hold officials in illegal means?

246
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:05,500
Then how about our laws and disciplines?

247
00:12:08,380 --> 00:12:09,260
Get up.

248
00:12:10,580 --> 00:12:11,540
Time to go.

249
00:12:26,980 --> 00:12:27,940
Hurry up.

250
00:12:29,620 --> 00:12:31,380
It’s the field officer of Zhenrong Army.

251
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:33,620
He’s in such a hurry.

252
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:35,220
Is it because

253
00:12:35,220 --> 00:12:36,500
Xixia are plundering on our border?

254
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,380
Mind your words, kid.

255
00:12:39,820 --> 00:12:41,500
We are being sent to Zhenrong Army.

256
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:43,620
We just need to do military service for a few years

257
00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:44,940
and then we can go home.

258
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:45,940
If there’s a war,

259
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:48,740
I didn’t commit a crime that deserves my life.

260
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:50,460
If you are killed,

261
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:53,020
will anyone from your family care for you?

262
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:55,460
If you can win some success and fame,

263
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:56,540
that will be worthy.

264
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:21,260
Your Majesty,

265
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:23,140
please have some.

266
00:13:28,620 --> 00:13:29,620
The Imperial Kitchen

267
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:32,060
knows Your Majesty is never a fan of extravagance,

268
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:34,700
so they never dare to seek for anything rare.

269
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:37,380
The son of the Governor of Zhanghua

270
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,980
sent it to the palace after the spring hunting.

271
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,500
He said

272
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:41,980
Your Majesty likes deer meat.

273
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:45,860
Shiyong stayed in the palace

274
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:47,140
for a couple of years when he was young.

275
00:13:47,940 --> 00:13:49,100
He is roughly the same age as me.

276
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:51,340
When we were young,

277
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:54,100
Her Majesty told him to call me grandfather.

278
00:13:55,260 --> 00:13:56,460
He cried out loud

279
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:57,620
feeling wronged.

280
00:13:58,540 --> 00:13:59,420
Later,

281
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:03,020
he was naughty and not good at studying.

282
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,260
I wrote a lot of articles for him.

283
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:06,660
Then he was willing

284
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:08,060
to call me grandfather.

285
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:24,420
This dried deer meat

286
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,620
is not as good as what the Empress made.

287
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:32,340
Go to the Hall of Peace

288
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:34,260
and ask if she still has

289
00:14:34,260 --> 00:14:35,020
the Moyao wine.

290
00:14:35,900 --> 00:14:37,260
Shiyong sent deer meat here,

291
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,180
did they make

292
00:14:39,180 --> 00:14:40,340
any dried deer meat?

293
00:14:42,700 --> 00:14:43,380
Yes, Your Majesty.

294
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:48,820
Tomorrow the kids will perform Nuo Dance first

295
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:49,980
before our show

296
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:50,860
Beauties Cutting Peonies.

297
00:14:52,340 --> 00:14:53,180
Sit.

298
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:57,380
Tomorrow is a private party.

299
00:14:58,020 --> 00:14:58,860
So we’ll dance

300
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:00,260
in front of His Majesty and Her Highness.

301
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:03,220
We will see

302
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:05,060
His Majesty and all the royal families this time.

303
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:08,340
Think about it,

304
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,020
we haven’t seen His Majesty

305
00:15:10,900 --> 00:15:11,860
after being in the palace

306
00:15:11,860 --> 00:15:12,940
for 2 years.

307
00:15:13,660 --> 00:15:14,980
I saw him in distance

308
00:15:15,420 --> 00:15:16,580
last year.

309
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:19,100
I heard he has a nice looking,

310
00:15:19,140 --> 00:15:20,180
just like someone in the painting.

311
00:15:20,180 --> 00:15:20,940
Really?

312
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:25,900
= Zhang Bihan =

313
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:29,500
Zhang Bihan is the best dancer

314
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:32,100
with a good looking and diligence.

315
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:36,020
No wonder Instructor Jia is biased to her,

316
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:39,220
letting her lead the dance even
if she is the youngest.

317
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:42,300
Diligence?

318
00:15:43,540 --> 00:15:46,060
= Xu Lantiao =
I think she is just being opportunistic,

319
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:47,260
hoping to reach the sky in a single bound.

320
00:15:51,860 --> 00:15:53,100
Someone is just obsessed

321
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,820
with flying up

322
00:15:54,820 --> 00:15:56,100
to a higher branch.

323
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:59,300
She even lied that she has met with His Majesty

324
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:01,660
in order to lure His Majesty.

325
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:05,900
Unfortunately His Majesty said he doesn’t know her.

326
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:10,060
And even so,

327
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:12,820
she feels no shame to show up
in front of His Majesty.

328
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,740
How humiliating she is!

329
00:16:21,820 --> 00:16:24,300
What, I’m simply telling the truth!

330
00:16:40,300 --> 00:16:41,740
I’m not telling a lie!

331
00:16:45,660 --> 00:16:46,780
-Stop it. - Stop it!

332
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:48,740
-Stop it! - Stop it!

333
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:51,860
Her Highness said,

334
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:52,980
she still has four pots of wine,

335
00:16:53,140 --> 00:16:54,220
and told me to bring all of them.

336
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:56,460
If Your Majesty still want more,

337
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:57,540
just tell her.

338
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:01,060
She didn’t make dried deer meat,

339
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,420
but if you like the taste

340
00:17:03,620 --> 00:17:04,580
of what they made before,

341
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:06,580
Her Highness has asked someone to write down

342
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:08,100
the recipe

343
00:17:08,580 --> 00:17:09,580
and sent it to the Imperial Kitchen.

344
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:18,500
Your Majesty,

345
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:20,660
is the wine enough?

346
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:24,260
Enough.

347
00:17:24,420 --> 00:17:25,420
You can go now.

348
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:26,820
Yes, Your Majesty.

349
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:49,820
= Dan =

350
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:51,940
Tomorrow is Huirou’s hundred-day,

351
00:17:53,420 --> 00:17:54,620
and you haven’t been here

352
00:17:54,620 --> 00:17:55,940
for almost a hundred days.

353
00:17:57,820 --> 00:18:00,100
How long are you going to punish yourself?

354
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:06,940
I didn’t make up anything.

355
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:10,420
I didn’t lie.

356
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,380
I heard you.

357
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,900
I didn’t lie.

358
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:16,740
Alright, I heard you.

359
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,880
= Instructor, Jia Yulan =

360
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:19,220
Go back and have a rest.

361
00:18:20,020 --> 00:18:20,780
I got it.

362
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:24,820
If you don’t believe me

363
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:28,180
just punish me and send me out.

364
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:30,300
I won’t complain anything.

365
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:32,420
I will always remember the kindness

366
00:18:32,420 --> 00:18:33,620
you’ve given to me for all those years.

367
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:36,900
My dear,

368
00:18:37,780 --> 00:18:39,460
only you two can be the center of the flower.

369
00:18:39,740 --> 00:18:41,620
Even if I want to punish you

370
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:43,300
and send you out

371
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:44,140
for scalding her face,

372
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:45,340
I have to wait after tomorrow

373
00:18:45,620 --> 00:18:47,660
you dance for the princess’ hundred-day
celebration.

374
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:53,500
Let me have a look.

375
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,780
Fortunately it’s just some scratch,

376
00:18:59,420 --> 00:19:00,540
plaster my medicine

377
00:19:00,540 --> 00:19:01,420
on it.

378
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:05,060
Don’t let it swell tomorrow.

379
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:10,820
I won’t dance.

380
00:19:13,180 --> 00:19:14,100
What did you say?

381
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:17,300
I won’t dance

382
00:19:18,540 --> 00:19:19,540
in tomorrow’s celebration.

383
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:22,460
If he says he doesn’t know me,

384
00:19:22,980 --> 00:19:24,380
then I will never see him again.

385
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:31,580
What’s wrong with you?

386
00:19:32,820 --> 00:19:33,860
Say it again?

387
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:36,420
He? Him?

388
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:37,900
Can you just call His Majesty that?

389
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:39,060
You bastard!

390
00:19:40,060 --> 00:19:41,540
You just can’t get over with it.

391
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:44,700
What a useless idiot!

392
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:46,940
Ms. Jia, you know me the best.

393
00:19:48,100 --> 00:19:49,820
Bihan is not a clever girl,

394
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:51,540
but I never lie.

395
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:53,780
I joined the institute

396
00:19:53,780 --> 00:19:55,420
just so that I can come to the palace

397
00:19:55,740 --> 00:19:57,420
and have the chance to see the person

398
00:19:57,420 --> 00:19:58,820
who I can never forget.

399
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:01,020
Before I didn’t know who he is,

400
00:20:01,660 --> 00:20:02,620
and now I finally met him,

401
00:20:02,620 --> 00:20:03,620
but he forgot me.

402
00:20:05,220 --> 00:20:06,900
I don’t want to see him anymore.

403
00:20:10,420 --> 00:20:11,420
Are you crazy?

404
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:15,100
You lost your mind?

405
00:20:15,540 --> 00:20:16,220
Did you?

406
00:20:16,220 --> 00:20:17,260
Answer me!

407
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,500
After I raised you for so many years,

408
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:21,420
what did I get in return?

409
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:25,820
Ms. Jia,

410
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:27,900
the cloak of His Majesty

411
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:28,900
is still in my room.

412
00:20:29,460 --> 00:20:30,820
Please give it to him for me.

413
00:20:31,100 --> 00:20:31,900
Stop!

414
00:20:32,180 --> 00:20:33,460
How dare you are!

415
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:37,860
You really don’t know what’s good for yourself.

416
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:39,220
That’s a cloak

417
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:39,900
from His Majesty.

418
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,140
His Majesty!

419
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:48,500
His Majesty

420
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:51,620
has been really nice to you.

421
00:20:53,820 --> 00:20:55,660
He gave you the cloak out of kindness,

422
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:58,100
but he didn’t need to listen to your nagging

423
00:20:58,260 --> 00:20:59,380
in the cold weather outside

424
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:00,420
for more than an hour.

425
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:20,180
You have such a good looking
and high dancing skills.

426
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:24,580
I hope I’ve chosen the right person.

427
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:03,700
Danshu,

428
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:07,100
Here you are.

429
00:22:44,860 --> 00:22:45,620
Come here.

430
00:22:56,130 --> 00:22:56,900
Huirou.

431
00:23:01,060 --> 00:23:01,860
Huirou.

432
00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:03,780
Look at the kid in the middle，

433
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:05,620
she’s playing Kuixiu

434
00:23:05,660 --> 00:23:06,540
in the twenty-eight stars.

435
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:08,700
The principle graduate

436
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:10,020
in our Imperial Examination

437
00:23:10,580 --> 00:23:12,340
is also called Kuishou.

438
00:23:12,460 --> 00:23:13,380
Both have the same pronunciation.

439
00:23:40,460 --> 00:23:41,940
What a jubilant and joyful dance.

440
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:43,500
Excellent.

441
00:23:47,860 --> 00:23:49,020
Huirou is happy too.

442
00:23:51,460 --> 00:23:52,180
Huan.

443
00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:53,180
Yes, Your Highness.

444
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:55,500
Award an embroidered pouch

445
00:23:56,020 --> 00:23:57,100
with a large copper coin,

446
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:58,740
a pair of lion candy

447
00:23:59,500 --> 00:24:01,180
and a dish of candied fruits

448
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:02,260
to each kid.

449
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:03,620
Yes, Your Highness.

450
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:16,900
I remember on the programme

451
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:20,740
there’s a dance called Beauties Cutting Peonies,

452
00:24:21,340 --> 00:24:23,140
a new show from the Institute this year.

453
00:24:23,460 --> 00:24:24,580
Why is it not here?

454
00:24:27,220 --> 00:24:28,100
Your Highness,

455
00:24:29,380 --> 00:24:30,460
there are two girls

456
00:24:30,820 --> 00:24:31,860
who can play the center of the flower.

457
00:24:32,420 --> 00:24:34,540
One of them

458
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:36,580
was injured last night,

459
00:24:36,820 --> 00:24:37,820
so she can’t dance.

460
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:39,100
The other one...

461
00:24:40,940 --> 00:24:43,380
The other one is spoiled

462
00:24:44,220 --> 00:24:44,900
and said she won’t dance

463
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,420
or eat

464
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:48,580
because

465
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:51,140
she had some grievance.

466
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:51,940
She also said

467
00:24:53,540 --> 00:24:55,420
she is not afraid of being sent out.

468
00:24:57,940 --> 00:24:58,620
Your Highness,

469
00:24:58,940 --> 00:25:00,340
I didn’t do my duty

470
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:01,940
to instruct them.

471
00:25:02,460 --> 00:25:03,660
Please punish me.

472
00:25:05,460 --> 00:25:07,060
It’s just a private party.

473
00:25:07,620 --> 00:25:08,580
You don’t deserve to be punished

474
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:10,700
for one dance.

475
00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:13,140
But you are the leader

476
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:14,420
of many young girls,

477
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:16,420
you should teach them

478
00:25:17,260 --> 00:25:18,700
to make them sensible,

479
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:20,060
gentle and humble.

480
00:25:20,660 --> 00:25:21,780
This is what all girls

481
00:25:21,980 --> 00:25:24,140
in the palace need to be.

482
00:25:25,420 --> 00:25:28,100
She should be able to bear some grievance.

483
00:25:30,700 --> 00:25:31,380
Yes, Your Highness.

484
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,500
I shall remember that.

485
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:38,060
-I - I

486
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,740
shall remember Your Highness’s instructions.

487
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:49,340
The spoiled and naughty girl

488
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:51,980
you mentioned just now,

489
00:25:52,420 --> 00:25:55,060
is Zhang Bihan

490
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:03,060
who was practicing in the back yard few days ago?

491
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:07,460
Yes.

492
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,740
I’ve instructed so many girls,

493
00:26:18,140 --> 00:26:20,260
but your looking is among the top three

494
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,780
in these years.

495
00:26:22,660 --> 00:26:23,900
Plus your personality

496
00:26:24,620 --> 00:26:25,860
makes you unique

497
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:27,140
and different.

498
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:32,420
Don’t you always criticize me

499
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:34,020
for misbehaving and willfulness,

500
00:26:34,500 --> 00:26:35,780
saying I am naughty?

501
00:26:38,700 --> 00:26:41,420
All the girls His Majesty met

502
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:42,820
are gentle, obedient,

503
00:26:43,140 --> 00:26:44,900
behaving well

504
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:47,180
with good manners.

505
00:26:48,540 --> 00:26:50,260
But eventually

506
00:26:50,380 --> 00:26:51,340
he will get tired of it.

507
00:26:53,540 --> 00:26:54,420
What?

508
00:26:59,020 --> 00:27:00,260
Do you like His Majesty

509
00:27:00,700 --> 00:27:01,700
and want to be his woman?

510
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:12,980
I do.

511
00:27:16,420 --> 00:27:17,940
I want to be the woman he loves most

512
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:20,820
in his entire life.

513
00:27:25,140 --> 00:27:26,540
Did Your Highness rest?

514
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:27,860
His Majesty is here.

515
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:34,900
Coming.

516
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:43,380
Light up the stove

517
00:27:43,380 --> 00:27:45,180
and boil some water and heat up the tea.

518
00:27:45,540 --> 00:27:46,220
Yes.

519
00:27:51,820 --> 00:27:52,540
Your Majesty.

520
00:27:53,100 --> 00:27:53,780
Come here.

521
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:03,660
The dishes in the celebration

522
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:04,500
were too greasy,

523
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:06,060
and the desserts

524
00:28:06,340 --> 00:28:07,380
were too sweet.

525
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:09,180
I got some fruit tea

526
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,420
from Xinhe,

527
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:11,260
and felt refreshed.

528
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:13,100
I thought you don’t like greasy and sweet stuff,

529
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:14,380
so I brought you some.

530
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:19,380
Thank you, Your Majesty.

531
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,980
There’s no one else.

532
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:25,820
You don’t need to bow or thank me

533
00:28:25,820 --> 00:28:26,780
every time you say something.

534
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:28,860
Come here, sit.

535
00:28:30,060 --> 00:28:30,780
Sit.

536
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,300
Thank you, Your Majesty.

537
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:43,660
I understand your kindness.

538
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:51,620
Some tea can’t be called as kindness.

539
00:28:52,900 --> 00:28:53,660
Actually,

540
00:28:54,300 --> 00:28:55,700
you also have the tea

541
00:28:56,740 --> 00:28:58,140
Xinhe made.

542
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:01,300
Thank you for comforting me

543
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:02,700
with the excuse of bringing me some tea.

544
00:29:11,340 --> 00:29:12,300
In the celebration,

545
00:29:12,620 --> 00:29:14,340
I told the instructor to teach girls

546
00:29:14,700 --> 00:29:16,660
to be sensible.

547
00:29:17,540 --> 00:29:18,500
But Your Majesty suddenly

548
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:20,420
asked about the naughty girl.

549
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:23,860
I was afraid at that time.

550
00:29:24,780 --> 00:29:25,900
I didn’t know if I

551
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:27,460
did or said something wrong.

552
00:29:30,060 --> 00:29:31,180
Then what do you think

553
00:29:32,180 --> 00:29:33,340
you said wrong?

554
00:29:43,020 --> 00:29:43,860
I am unintelligent.

555
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:46,620
After I thought about it over and over again,

556
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:48,500
I didn’t think I said or did

557
00:29:49,420 --> 00:29:50,660
anything wrong

558
00:29:51,340 --> 00:29:52,660
or anything disgraceful.

559
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:57,460
Yes,

560
00:29:57,820 --> 00:29:59,940
you are always tolerant,

561
00:30:00,220 --> 00:30:01,460
elegant and wise.

562
00:30:01,660 --> 00:30:02,700
How can you be wrong?

563
00:30:03,420 --> 00:30:06,900
Then I am the one who was wrong.

564
00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:24,900
Your Majesty is the lord of the world,

565
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:26,380
you manage everything around the world.

566
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,500
What you see, you think and you do

567
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:31,220
is not things I can understand,

568
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,100
let alone to conjecture.

569
00:30:33,100 --> 00:30:34,820
Your Majesty must have your reason

570
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:37,260
to do this and say that.

571
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:38,860
What I can do

572
00:30:39,140 --> 00:30:39,940
is to follow the conventions from ancestors

573
00:30:39,940 --> 00:30:41,340
and disciplines in the harem

574
00:30:41,540 --> 00:30:42,380
as I am supposed to

575
00:30:42,620 --> 00:30:43,660
and constantly review myself,

576
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,340
to fulfill my duty as an empress.

577
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:47,780
If you are still not satisfied,

578
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:49,380
then it must be because

579
00:30:49,380 --> 00:30:50,260
I am not smart enough,

580
00:30:51,340 --> 00:30:54,180
and I shall take any punishment you give me.

581
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:28,660
See Your Majesty out.

582
00:31:45,740 --> 00:31:46,620
What’s wrong?

583
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:50,460
Liaozi said

584
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:52,020
recently

585
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:53,540
you have been treating His Majesty coldly.

586
00:31:53,860 --> 00:31:54,900
His Majesty was quite upset

587
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:56,940
and humiliated you

588
00:31:57,100 --> 00:31:58,340
during the celebration with some willfulness.

589
00:31:58,420 --> 00:31:59,820
His Majesty felt bad about it after he’s back

590
00:32:00,540 --> 00:32:02,380
and sent Liaozi to bring you some tea.

591
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:03,780
But before Liaozi went out,

592
00:32:04,300 --> 00:32:05,180
His Majesty said

593
00:32:05,380 --> 00:32:07,260
he hadn’t come here for some time,

594
00:32:07,700 --> 00:32:09,220
so he came here along.

595
00:32:10,740 --> 00:32:11,540
What’s wrong?

596
00:32:20,340 --> 00:32:21,700
His Majesty has always been benevolent

597
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:23,540
and he likes you

598
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,420
and cares about you.

599
00:32:25,340 --> 00:32:26,620
We go to him recklessly

600
00:32:26,620 --> 00:32:27,620
like this.

601
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:31,460
I guess even if he doesn’t want to see you,

602
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:32,820
he won’t punish you anyway.

603
00:32:34,540 --> 00:32:35,900
But things are unpredictable.

604
00:32:35,900 --> 00:32:36,900
We are being too reckless.

605
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:38,020
No matter what it turns out to be,

606
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:40,900
I will still appreciate your kindness to me.

607
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:46,140
Huan,

608
00:32:49,980 --> 00:32:51,900
am I being too harsh

609
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:54,980
boring

610
00:32:55,580 --> 00:32:56,940
and scaring?

611
00:32:58,100 --> 00:32:59,580
You are always the smartest

612
00:32:59,660 --> 00:33:00,860
and educated girl.

613
00:33:01,220 --> 00:33:02,580
Previously,

614
00:33:02,900 --> 00:33:04,580
when the lord and madam were upset,

615
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:06,220
or when your brother was naughty,

616
00:33:06,820 --> 00:33:08,780
you could always make them happy or manage them.

617
00:33:09,620 --> 00:33:10,820
Even your uncle,

618
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:12,620
the general everyone admires at the court

619
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:14,180
likes you so much.

620
00:33:15,500 --> 00:33:17,620
But you only care about rules

621
00:33:18,140 --> 00:33:19,660
and refuse to take a step back

622
00:33:19,980 --> 00:33:21,060
in front of His Majesty.

623
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:23,260
Don’t you remember

624
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:25,900
our madam can never win over the lord with words.

625
00:33:26,740 --> 00:33:29,620
But as soon as she cried, got angry

626
00:33:30,020 --> 00:33:32,300
or said something nice to him,

627
00:33:32,940 --> 00:33:34,220
he could always humor her.

628
00:33:34,620 --> 00:33:35,340
Right?

629
00:33:40,140 --> 00:33:42,540
But my parents are an ordinary couple.

630
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:44,340
Me and His Majesty...

631
00:33:44,540 --> 00:33:46,140
You are the national father and mother.

632
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:47,500
But that’s how others see you,

633
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:50,060
you are his wife to His Majesty.

634
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:51,580
Besides,

635
00:33:52,100 --> 00:33:52,940
today His Majesty

636
00:33:52,980 --> 00:33:54,340
came here to humor you,

637
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:56,700
why can’t you do the same to him?

638
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:06,220
Then give me the calligraphy

639
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:08,300
I was most satisfied with

640
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:10,700
and a pot of Moyao.

641
00:34:12,100 --> 00:34:13,580
Okay, on my way.

642
00:34:26,100 --> 00:34:27,020
Once I was back,

643
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:29,780
I criticized her for an hour

644
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:32,060
with Her Highness’ instructions.

645
00:34:32,780 --> 00:34:33,820
She didn’t say anything

646
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:35,780
and only asked

647
00:34:36,780 --> 00:34:38,020
what Your Majesty said.

648
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,060
Well...

649
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:40,660
I did not dare to hide

650
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:43,220
anything Your Majesty said,

651
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:44,380
and told her every word.

652
00:34:46,380 --> 00:34:48,420
But she

653
00:34:48,420 --> 00:34:50,420
begged me to take her to see Your Majesty.

654
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:53,420
I’ve criticized her and said nice things to her,

655
00:34:54,100 --> 00:34:56,180
but she insisted to come,

656
00:34:56,740 --> 00:34:58,740
saying if I don’t take her

657
00:34:58,740 --> 00:34:59,620
to Your Majesty,

658
00:34:59,620 --> 00:35:01,020
she will find a way anyway.

659
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:03,220
I know how

660
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:04,740
perseverant she is.

661
00:35:04,740 --> 00:35:05,940
She is not afraid of anything.

662
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:10,300
If I send her out,

663
00:35:10,500 --> 00:35:11,900
Your Majesty told me

664
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:12,940
not to be harsh on her.

665
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:14,340
I do not dare to go against your command.

666
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:18,060
So I have no choice but to

667
00:35:18,260 --> 00:35:20,020
beg Deputy Officer Yang

668
00:35:20,020 --> 00:35:21,300
to send Your Majesty a message.

669
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:24,500
If I disturbed Your Majesty,

670
00:35:25,180 --> 00:35:27,380
I can’t be punished enough.

671
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:45,260
What do you want to say

672
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:47,500
in person?

673
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:51,140
I didn’t lie.

674
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:53,180
I saw you before.

675
00:35:53,500 --> 00:35:54,060
You!

676
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:55,580
You reckless

677
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:56,260
idiot!

678
00:35:56,540 --> 00:35:57,460
Forgive her, Your Majesty.

679
00:35:58,020 --> 00:35:58,900
Forgive her, Your Majesty.

680
00:36:00,020 --> 00:36:01,180
I knew this already.

681
00:36:04,180 --> 00:36:05,100
No one said you were lying.

682
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:05,740
Yes,

683
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:10,420
they said I was lying,

684
00:36:10,820 --> 00:36:12,060
I was being silly,

685
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:13,100
and I wanted to fly to a higher branch.

686
00:36:13,700 --> 00:36:14,900
I practiced so hard.

687
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:17,700
They said I was rejected by you,

688
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:20,380
and also mocked at me.

689
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:30,700
I practiced so hard

690
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,140
because I want to dance for you.

691
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:35,100
I don’t have any intention

692
00:36:35,140 --> 00:36:36,500
just because I like you.

693
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:39,340
Do you want His Majesty to

694
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:41,420
comment on your Flying White Seal Script?

695
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:42,900
And we brought Moyao

696
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:44,380
to write more floating characters

697
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:45,900
with the wine?

698
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,540
Let’s call it the gift to the master.

699
00:36:52,700 --> 00:36:53,420
Stand up.

700
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:55,540
Stand up.

701
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:02,260
You too.

702
00:37:04,180 --> 00:37:05,180
Thank you, Your Majesty.

703
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:15,420
You can’t control

704
00:37:16,380 --> 00:37:18,260
what other people say

705
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:21,060
or talk.

706
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:22,020
Even I

707
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:24,380
can’t control what they want to say.

708
00:37:25,540 --> 00:37:26,420
Besides,

709
00:37:27,620 --> 00:37:29,540
that girl was hurt by you.

710
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:31,460
You’ve vented your anger,

711
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:33,220
but why didn’t you come to the celebration

712
00:37:33,340 --> 00:37:35,260
to dance?

713
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:37,060
How am I supposed to know

714
00:37:37,060 --> 00:37:37,740
if Your Majesty

715
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:39,020
is someone like them?

716
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:41,260
If I went to dance with hope

717
00:37:41,740 --> 00:37:43,220
but you were laughing at me in your heart

718
00:37:43,220 --> 00:37:44,260
and looking down upon me?

719
00:37:50,100 --> 00:37:51,460
What silly ideas

720
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:52,620
do you have in your mind?

721
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:56,140
Alright, alright,

722
00:37:56,860 --> 00:37:57,860
you don’t want me to laugh at you.

723
00:37:58,460 --> 00:37:59,900
Then why did you change your mind

724
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:01,140
and force Ms. Jia

725
00:38:01,140 --> 00:38:02,140
to take you to see me?

726
00:38:03,580 --> 00:38:04,820
Once Ms. Jia was back,

727
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:06,940
she criticized me,

728
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:09,300
and I only asked if Your Majesty criticized me.

729
00:38:09,820 --> 00:38:11,820
She told me what you said.

730
00:38:12,900 --> 00:38:13,860
You might worried about

731
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:16,540
that I might have been wronged.

732
00:38:29,180 --> 00:38:30,100
Alright, alright,

733
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:31,460
now you know

734
00:38:32,460 --> 00:38:33,420
I didn’t laugh at you

735
00:38:33,420 --> 00:38:34,460
or look down upon you.

736
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:37,020
The one who wronged you

737
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:38,100
was hurt.

738
00:38:38,740 --> 00:38:39,660
So now

739
00:38:39,940 --> 00:38:41,500
don’t get upset about it.

740
00:38:45,020 --> 00:38:45,740
Your Majesty,

741
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:47,820
do you really forget me?

742
00:38:53,460 --> 00:38:55,580
What Your Majesty think about is all the people

743
00:38:56,020 --> 00:38:57,420
and state affairs.

744
00:38:58,820 --> 00:39:00,260
Unlike me,

745
00:39:01,340 --> 00:39:02,700
my encounter with Your Majesty

746
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,140
is the thing that is worth

747
00:39:04,140 --> 00:39:05,420
remembering in my whole life.

748
00:39:09,900 --> 00:39:10,740
Now I know you

749
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:13,580
and won’t forget.

750
00:39:16,620 --> 00:39:17,340
Really?

751
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:20,020
I mean what I said.

752
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:23,340
Then I want to dance for you.

753
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:25,460
I don’t want you to remember me

754
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:26,940
as a crying girl.

755
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:29,060
I want you to remember

756
00:39:29,660 --> 00:39:30,860
the best of me.

757
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:49,470
♪ You are like the cloud in the sky ♪

758
00:39:50,770 --> 00:39:57,320
♪ I am like the bird in the cloud ♪

759
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:05,590
♪ I go wherever you go ♪

760
00:40:06,830 --> 00:40:14,310
♪ In the sunshine and breeze ♪

761
00:40:26,300 --> 00:40:27,700
Will I disturb His Majesty from work?

762
00:40:29,260 --> 00:40:31,140
His Majesty didn’t summon anyone,

763
00:40:31,420 --> 00:40:32,100
but

764
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:33,460
that...

765
00:40:38,220 --> 00:40:40,060
His Majesty, how’s my dance?

766
00:40:46,180 --> 00:40:47,940
You turned a stepping song into a solo dance.

767
00:40:48,700 --> 00:40:50,140
That’s very unique.

768
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:51,260
Great.

769
00:40:57,180 --> 00:40:59,100
I didn’t know Your Majesty have a guest

770
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:00,700
until I was in the hall.

771
00:41:01,620 --> 00:41:02,620
Sorry to interrupt.

772
00:41:06,580 --> 00:41:07,740
What a coincidence.

773
00:41:11,060 --> 00:41:13,700
This is the girl who didn’t come to dance

774
00:41:13,780 --> 00:41:14,980
in today’s celebration.

775
00:41:15,580 --> 00:41:18,100
The instructor took her here for punishment.

776
00:41:19,100 --> 00:41:19,900
Take a seat.

777
00:41:34,380 --> 00:41:36,660
Your Highness, I am dancer Zhang Bihan.

778
00:41:39,820 --> 00:41:40,740
This girl

779
00:41:41,260 --> 00:41:43,420
is the naughty girl

780
00:41:43,700 --> 00:41:45,220
I mentioned in the celebration.

781
00:41:45,820 --> 00:41:48,580
I was incapable to teach her well.

782
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:52,700
Your Highness,
please show me the correct instructions.

783
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:59,100
His Majesty didn’t summon them.

784
00:41:59,580 --> 00:42:00,700
Deputy Officer Yang

785
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:02,460
kept them waiting outside of the hall

786
00:42:02,780 --> 00:42:03,900
to see His Majesty,

787
00:42:04,780 --> 00:42:06,620
saying the girl was crying

788
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:08,060
and refused to eat or drink anything.

789
00:42:08,460 --> 00:42:10,340
She insisted to apologize to His Majesty in person.

790
00:42:12,180 --> 00:42:13,420
This girl is very persistent.

791
00:42:13,780 --> 00:42:14,940
Even the instructor couldn’t manage her

792
00:42:15,180 --> 00:42:16,380
and was afraid that something might happen,

793
00:42:17,420 --> 00:42:18,860
so she begged Deputy Officer Yang.

794
00:42:19,500 --> 00:42:20,420
If everyone can meet His Majesty

795
00:42:20,780 --> 00:42:22,140
simply by crying and refusing to eat,

796
00:42:22,540 --> 00:42:23,660
the gate of the palace will be overcrowded

797
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:25,300
let alone the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

798
00:42:27,180 --> 00:42:27,980
I don’t think

799
00:42:28,140 --> 00:42:29,140
she will starve herself to death

800
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:30,500
if His Majesty doesn’t see her.

801
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:46,860
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

802
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:56,540
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

803
00:42:59,380 --> 00:43:04,100
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

804
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:09,240
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

805
00:43:10,680 --> 00:43:16,160
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

806
00:43:16,160 --> 00:43:20,950
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

807
00:43:24,610 --> 00:43:30,250
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

808
00:43:30,250 --> 00:43:35,160
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

809
00:43:35,660 --> 00:43:41,420
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

810
00:43:41,420 --> 00:43:46,510
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

811
00:43:46,940 --> 00:43:51,870
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

812
00:43:52,490 --> 00:43:57,340
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

813
00:43:58,030 --> 00:44:03,180
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

814
00:44:03,680 --> 00:44:08,720
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

815
00:44:09,260 --> 00:44:13,330
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

816
00:44:14,800 --> 00:44:19,440
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

817
00:44:20,460 --> 00:44:25,620
♪ The howling wind ♪

818
00:44:25,990 --> 00:44:30,060
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

819
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:36,460
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

820
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:42,340
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

821
00:44:42,760 --> 00:44:48,040
♪ The howling wind ♪

822
00:44:48,330 --> 00:44:53,230
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

823
00:44:53,820 --> 00:45:00,530
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
